id: pm-5dia
title: Add extension adopt workflow for unmanaged extensions
description: Introduce a lightweight adoption path so existing unmanaged project/global extensions can be registered as managed without reinstalling.
type: Task
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[4]: adoption,extensions,external-audit,pm-cli
created_at: "2026-04-05T01:12:30.369Z"
updated_at: "2026-04-05T03:47:37.681Z"
author: codex-agent
acceptance_criteria: "pm extension supports adopt for existing unmanaged extensions, writes deterministic managed metadata including source/ref/provenance fields when available, and extension doctor/manage surfaces reflect managed update-check eligibility."
parent: pm-gt8u
comments[5]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-05T01:12:30.369Z",codex-agent,"Duplicate-check evidence: pm context --limit 10; pm search 'extension adopt unmanaged managed metadata' --limit 10; pm search 'extension manage skipped_unmanaged' --limit 10; pm list-open --limit 80; pm list-in-progress --limit 80. Net-new because existing extension diagnostics/management items cover doctor/manage status semantics but not adopt-without-reinstall workflow."
  "2026-04-05T02:18:03.973Z",codex-agent,"Implemented extension adopt end-to-end (CLI/contracts/Pi/completion/help/docs) and added adoption regressions including already-managed path. Evidence: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/extension-command.spec.ts tests/unit/extension-command-github.spec.ts tests/integration/help-runtime.spec.ts passed; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage passed with branch coverage 91.01%; pnpm build passed; repro probe confirms pm extension --help exposes --adopt/--doctor."
  "2026-04-05T03:08:02.560Z",codex-agent,"Reopened for external issue #3 ergonomic follow-up: add bulk unmanaged extension adoption flow (--adopt-all) while preserving existing --adopt behavior."
  "2026-04-05T03:23:51.529Z",codex-agent,"Progress: implemented bulk unmanaged adoption via pm extension --adopt-all with deterministic bulk record creation, no-target/no-source-option validation, and parity wiring across CLI, completion, SDK contracts, and Pi wrapper. Added unit coverage for adopt-all lifecycle and validation guards."
  "2026-04-05T03:46:58.712Z",codex-agent,"Added pm extension --adopt-all bulk adoption flow with argument guards, deterministic adoption summary, completion/contracts/Pi wiring, and tests."
